{"tid":1710251,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實要停止呢場運動係睇你班港豬敢唔敢罷工，而唔係睇政府去做啲乜","createTime":"2019-11-12T06:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T07:42:20.000Z","uid":292024,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4d235e9a22f5ae46e1d381388f3d873a0cc71d","tid":1710251,"uid":292024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"班學生已經不顧性命去守護香港民主自由，柒婆對呢兩日行動已經驚到瀨屎，連出兩日見記者，全港罷工係唯一出路，勇武已經根疲力盡，和理非係時候全面進場<br />\n<br />\n1.公務員所謂政治中立只係俾政府制抓住你地做佢地防盾，公務員大罷工癱瘓政府先係呢場運動勝負關鍵，請唔好再講政治中立<br />\n<br />\n2.運輸業，主宰所有港豬返工既權力，只要你地停駛就可以制造被罷工，唔洗再要班年青人去犧牲性命<br />\n<br />\n3.港豬唔好再睇眼前利益，返少日工賺少左錢，你地唔肯罷工等同要送班年青人去死，殺害年青人係港豬，而唔係呢個政府，隔日罷工都好，唔好再咁自私<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可，光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n利申：呢兩日都冇返工"},{"pid":"a218e18368cce157e2df19cf0b337cf70d786ba8","tid":1710251,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d5c4c93dd71db15a45321ffe21bfc26f6e4054","tid":1710251,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450dd5f77790265b9d81a846e96a9d7da3038b6c","tid":1710251,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca399897076249eb0c424a07a25db11c82ec7ed0","tid":1710251,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9732a293b02df786ec6d5a97ad0c6f501d3ed7","tid":1710251,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:32:01.000Z","msg":"港豬 俾柒婆笑你地返工好勤力哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9544c75a3cc591c11ad305417a903925db212bc8","tid":1710251,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:32:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>777根本好驚你哋罷工罷課</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8a13acbc8a7595e6c63bc20d6a6d72f562772c9c","tid":1710251,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:32:35.000Z","msg":"專業操守=畀人㩒住屌任做，賤撚過雞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efac52c1ed65caae05af4a98257179d8376c999","tid":1710251,"uid":271676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:37:01.000Z","msg":"公務員好多都藍到仆街<br />\n朋友成日呻對住d藍絲好辛苦<br />\n公務員罷工係好大威力 <br />\n但要係我地自己友滲透得夠多先有用"},{"pid":"9ef5f0b140249acacd324e4c0054df269f2102af","tid":1710251,"uid":292024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca399897076249eb0c424a07a25db11c82ec7ed0","tid":1710251,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:41:49.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11312531304f22ecf9fc0832a7b672214e71ab45","tid":1710251,"uid":292024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df9732a293b02df786ec6d5a97ad0c6f501d3ed7","tid":1710251,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:32:01.000Z","msg":"港豬 俾柒婆笑你地返工好勤力哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:42:00.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029fb9fa0546f52faaadf3469d10beecbc7ed635","tid":1710251,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986eb6af7c563b53807fbab09bc16229ed073737","tid":1710251,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":